%% ML Metadata - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipeline<br/>Component
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as Database Backend<br/>(MySQL 3306 / PostgreSQL 5432)
    participant UI as Pipeline UI /<br/>Client

    Note over KFP, DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    KFP->>MLMD: PutExecutionType<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS / mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT execution_type<br/>Optional TLS<br/>Username/Password Auth
    DB-->>MLMD: Type ID
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutExecutionTypeResponse

    KFP->>MLMD: PutExecution<br/>(with artifacts, events, contexts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT execution, artifacts,<br/>events, attributions<br/>(atomic transaction)
    DB-->>MLMD: IDs
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutExecutionResponse

    KFP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts<br/>(datasets, models)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE artifacts
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact IDs
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutArtifactsResponse

    Note over UI, DB: Flow 2: Metadata Query and Lineage Retrieval

    UI->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS / mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts<br/>JOIN attributions<br/>Optional TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact rows
    MLMD-->>UI: GetArtifactsByContextResponse

    UI->>MLMD: GetLineageGraph<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts, executions,<br/>events, contexts<br/>(graph traversal)
    DB-->>MLMD: Lineage data
    MLMD-->>UI: GetLineageGraphResponse
